It seems we are about to witness another marital union between Big Brother Naija housemates very soon. Few days after the wedding of Bambam and TeddyA, news broke out that ex-BBNaija housemates, Tobi Bakre and KimOprah secretly got engaged in Dubai. According to Grapevine info, the two are in a romantic relationship and have been going out for quite some time now. Tobi had also hinted to a possible union between the two with a post he made on Twitter few days ago revealing that he wanted to wait till 35 but now at 25 it is down. Well, most Big Brother Naija ex-housemates are crazy about grabbing the headlines and this could be just another attempt at seeking relevance. Source